Donovan Scott https://en.wikipedia.org/wiki/Donovan_Scott 0 Donovan Scott (born September 29, 1946) is an American character actor best known for his role as cadet Leslie Barbara in the 1984 film Police Academy, in which he was part of an ensemble cast led by Steve Guttenberg.
